2D-Array :
                          Columns
-----------------------------------------------------
|        |          |   0   |   1  |   2   |   3   |
|        |-------------------------------------------
|        |    0     |      |      |       |        |      
|        | ---------|------|------|-------|--------|
| Rows   |    1     |      |      |       |        |
|        |----------|------|------|-------|--------|  
|        |    2     |      |      |       |        |
|        |----------|------|------|-------|--------| 
|        |    3     |      |      |       |        |
|--------|------------------------------------------

*Features of 2D Array :-

* 2D Array provide a structured way to represent the data in rows and columns.
* THey are suitable for tabular data,grids,matrices where information needs to be organizied in a 2D format.
* Elements in a 2D array can be accessed using two indices - one for the row and one for columns.
* This allows for efficient data retrieval and manipulation,making 2D array ideal for tasks such as image processing and spreadsheet applications.
* The time complexity for 2D array is n.

